								<img src="images/girl-with-glasses.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="A girl with glasses reading a book with a drawn lighbulb over her head" />
							</a>
							<h3>Cognitive Assessments</h3>
							<p>A cognitive assessment can be helpful when a young person is struggling with learning in school or having difficulties in specific areas. The young person will engage in a series of activities/puzzles/tasks which have been specifically designed to gain a fuller understanding of a young person’s strengths and weaknesses in a variety of areas.</p>
							<a href="services.htm?serviceId=4" class="btn btn-secondary">Find out more...</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- End Cognitive Assessments Section -->
					
