					  <h3> Autism Assessment and Diagnosis Service in Sussex</h3>
					  <p>At Making Sense Of It, we have joined with Speech and Language Therapists (SALT) to offer a multidisciplinary assessment and diagnosis service. Giving an autism diagnosis to a child involves detailed and comprehensive assessment of all areas of their life. Our assessments follow NICE guidelines as closely as possible.</p>
					  <a href="services.htm?serviceId=5" class="btn btn-secondary">Find out more...</a>
